"You’ll help keep our nation moving every single day. A critical part of the work we do is the daily upkeep of the rail network. As a Senior Technical Officer your role is to provide day to day technical support for a wide variety of equipment across a large geographical area. A Senior Technical Officer works both in the office and outdoors on site, supporting essential maintenance to keep the railway running safely and smoothly for passengers and freight users. Our team members come from a variety of different backgrounds, and this might be the first time that you’ve even considered a career in rail. We’re focused on your transferrable skills and behaviours and if you can demonstrate that you are well suited, then we will provide you with all the necessary training to have you working safely and competently out on the network. And if you make the grade then you can look forward to a rewarding and fulfilling career with a company that recently joined the top 50 in the Glassdoor's 2021 Best Places to Work."